### Variables — adjust as needed
@host = http://localhost:8080
@username = alice
@password = secret123
@token = <paste token from POST /api/auth/token response>
@taskId = 1


### ─── Accounts ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register a new user
POST {{host}}/api/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}


### ─── Auth ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get a Bearer token (Basic auth — run this, copy token into @token above)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/token
Authorization: Basic {{username}} {{password}}


### ─── Tasks ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create a task
POST {{host}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Fix login bug",
  "description": "Users can't log in with special characters in their password."
}

### List all tasks
GET {{host}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List tasks filtered by author
GET {{host}}/api/tasks?author={{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List tasks filtered by assignee
GET {{host}}/api/tasks?assignee=bob
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Assign a task to a user
PUT {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/assign
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assignee": "bob"
}

### Update task status
PUT {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}


### ─── Comments ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Add a comment to a task
POST {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "Reproduced on Safari — looks like URL encoding is the culprit."
}

### List comments for a task
GET {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
